        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nNote that this change *currently* has no actual verification tests. I actually do intent to make some, so this change can be treated as WIP. At least it could be possible to verify existence of kubeconfig, check node status and so on. Currently it only runs the role itself in converge, like rancher playbook.",
